      <h1 class='title'>Water Framework Directive</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 July 2003 vol 409 c43WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_43ws' title='Col. 43WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 July 2003 vol 409 c43WS' name='column_43ws' href='#column_43ws' rel='bookmark'>43WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0409P0-02466'>
        <a name='S6CV0409P0_20030716_CWS_22'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-elliot-morley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0409P0_20030716_CWS_22' title='Link to this speech by Mr Elliot Morley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-elliot-morley" title="Mr Elliot Morley">The Minister for the Environment (Mr. Elliot Morley)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0409P0-02466">The Government intend to publish a third consultation paper on the water framework directive at the end of July or early August.</p><p id="S6CV0409P0-02467">This third consultation will contain proposed draft transposing regulations, a revised regulatory impact assessment and a summary of responses to the second consultation paper with the Government's response.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
